{"word":"ζωή","slug":"ζωή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ζωή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el>ζώω</el> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ζῶ\">ζῶ</a></el>)] <b>life<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> normal physical sense <b><a href='B:490 16:25'>Lk 16:25</a></b> (= lifetime); <b><a href='B:510 17:25'>Ac 17:25</a>; <a href='B:520 8:38'>Ro 8:38</a>; <a href='B:650 7:3'>Hb 7:3</a>; <a href='B:660 4:14'>Js 4:14</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a condition or experience transcending normal physical life <b><a href='B:470 7:14'>Mt 7:14</a>; <a href='B:470 18:8'>18:8</a>; <a href='B:480 10:30'>Mk 10:30</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in Mt and Mk <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔρχομαι\">ἔρχομαι</a></el>); <b><a href='B:500 1:4'>J 1:4</a>; <a href='B:500 3:15'>3:15f</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in J <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el>αἰώνιον</el>); <b><a href='B:500 6:35'>6:35</a>; <a href='B:510 2:28'>Ac 2:28</a>; <a href='B:510 5:20'>5:20</a>; <a href='B:510 11:18'>11:18</a>; <a href='B:520 5:17'>Ro 5:17</a>; <a href='B:520 8:6'>8:6</a>; <a href='B:530 3:22'>1 Cor 3:22</a>; <a href='B:540 4:10'>2 Cor 4:10</a>; <a href='B:560 4:18'>Eph 4:18</a>; <a href='B:570 4:3'>Phil 4:3</a>; <a href='B:610 4:8'>1 Ti 4:8</a>; <a href='B:650 7:16'>Hb 7:16</a>; <a href='B:660 1:12'>Js 1:12</a>; <a href='B:690 1:1'>1 J 1:1</a>; <a href='B:730 2:7'>Rv 2:7</a>; <a href='B:730 3:5'>3:5</a>; <a href='B:730 22:17'>22:17</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ζωγρέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ζώνη\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}